Colophon

Akademický theme for Jekyll, created by Eric M. Fink.

Based on al-folio, with elements from tufte-jekyll and tufte-pandoc-jekyll (sidenotes, marginnotes and figures in the style of Edward Tufte), and bijou (table and button styles).

Set in Portada and Adelle Sans by Veronika Burian & José Scaglione, and LFT Etica Mono by Leftloft.
